        'title' => 'Allowlist authorized libraries',
        'description' => 'Use technical controls to ensure that only authorized software libraries, such as specific .dll, .ocx, .so files, etc., are allowed to load into a system process. Block unauthorized libraries from loading into a system process. Reassess bi-annually, or more frequently.',
        'principle_id' => '2',
