        'code' => '164.410(b)',
        'title' => '164.410(b)',
        'description' => 'Except as provided in §164.412, a business associate shall provide the notification required by paragraph (a) of this section without unreasonable delay and in no case later than 60 calendar days after the discovery of a breach.',
