        'code' => 'Management (Control 2)',
        'title' => 'Designation Confirmation for Subprocessor Role',
        'description' => 'Where Microsoft confirms that your engagements fulfill a Subprocessor role, Supplier must have applicable data protection agreements in place with Microsoft.  

