        'title' => 'Monitoring Effectiveness of Preference Management',
        'description' => 'Websites that use cookies (and/or similar technologies that store or retrieve data from a device or otherwise similarly enable user tracking) must obtain legally-required consents from data subjects before cookies are used or placed in connection with data subjects’ browsers or devices.

