        'source' => 'vanta',
        'source_file' => 'resources/frameworks/vanta/raw/ofdss.json',
        'sort_order' => 3972,
        'context' => 'Appropriately scoped, and sufficiently verbose, logs can produce a lot of log entries, which can make their review challenging. Robust alerts allow an organization to zero-in on events that require attention (e.g. anomalies and drifts of expected behavior), and ignore events that do not (e.g. normal and expected behavior).',
    ],
    [
