        'source_file' => 'resources/frameworks/vanta/raw/ofdss.json',
        'sort_order' => 3976,
        'context' => 'The techniques used by attackers for phishing and other social engineering evolves over time. If employee awareness does not also evolve, then the organization will stand vulnerable to these attacks.
